revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{tsh|RIC}}
== Usage ==
This template gives a button to use [[Special:RandomInCategory]] to go to a random page in a category. It should be only used in the Category namespace; using it in other namespaces will return an error.

There is one optional parameter, <code>|text</code> which will change the text of the button.
<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line; interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Internal link templates]]
}}</includeonly>

